msgid "Yahtzee-like Dice Game"
msgstr "Juego de dados similar al Yahtzee"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kiriki.appdata.xml:12
msgid ""
"Kiriki is an addictive and fun dice game, designed to be played by as many "
"as six players. Participants have to collect points by rolling five dice for "
"up to three times per single turn."
msgstr ""
"Kiriki es un juego de dados divertido y adictivo en el que pueden participar "
"hasta seis jugadores. Los participantes deben reunir puntos tirando cinco "
"dados hasta tres veces en cada turno."
